title: Microsoft HoloLens 2
introContent: An ergonomic, untethered self-contained holographic device with enterprise-ready applications to increase user accuracy and output.

icons.title: Precision
icons.iconText: Stay engaged heads-up, hands-free longer and more comfortably to safely complete tasks error-free.

icons.iconText: Stay engaged heads-up, hands-free longer and more comfortably to safely complete tasks error-free.

icons.title: App Ecosystem

specs.title: Holographic density
specs.text: More than 2.5k radiants (light points per radian)
